data.meta_description: Carer benefits and legal services - Official information from NHS about The Royal Borough of Windsor and Maidenhead - services for adults including contact, directions and service details
data.text:
The Royal Borough of Windsor and Maidenhead - services for adults

About

Provide social care services for adults

Opening times

Monday to Friday 9am - 5pm

Catchment area

Windsor and Maidenhead

Target group

Adults and those that care for them

Further information

For a first time service user, please call The Front Door Team 01628 683744 option 1. For existing service users, please call the Community Social work Team 01628 683744 option 2. To report a safeguarding concern, please call 01628 683744 option 3.

Referral method

Self referral
